Class DiscoveryManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ubudu.iot.ble.DiscoveryManager

  • public class DiscoveryManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by julien on 4/26/17.

    This class is dedicated to finding the bluetooth device matching the given filter. Filter is defined by an object implementing BleDeviceFilter interface.
